title: Escaping Polygamy - Season 1
description:
Escaping Polygamy - Season 1

Escaping Polygamy focuses on the dramatic work of three sisters who escaped from the polygamous cult known as the Kingston clan as young women and now help other young men, women and children to escape, preferring to face hell than spend another day inside.

Ep 1 - Leah-Hannah
EP 2 - Melanie
Ep 3 - Kathy
Ep 4 - Rachel
Ep 5 - Priscilla
Ep 6 - Little Sister
Ep 7 - Yolanda
